# Cursor Settings for DateCalculatorPlus

## Project Configuration
```
projectName: "DateCalculatorPlus"
mainBranch: "main"
documentationRoot: "./development.md"
updateLog: "./cursor-updates.md"
```

## Core Documentation Files
```
documentationFiles:
  - README.md          # Project overview and quick start
  - development.md     # Comprehensive development guide
  - cursorrules.md     # Technical standards
  - cursor-updates.md  # Development progress tracking
  - deployment.md      # Deployment instructions
```

## Documentation Workflow
```
documentationWorkflow:
  # Avoid creating new markdown files for specific features
  consolidateDocs: true
  
  # Update existing docs instead of creating new ones
  preferExistingDocs: true
  
  # Use sections in development.md for specific topics
  useDevSections: true
  
  # Keep cursor-updates.md as development progress source of truth
  trackProgressIn: "cursor-updates.md"
  
  # Limit README.md updates to essential changes only
  limitReadmeUpdates: true
  
  # Run update script after making significant changes
  postUpdateCommand: "./update-cursor-date.sh"

## Editor Settings
```
editor:
  # Show line numbers for better documentation reference
  lineNumbers: true
  
  # Enable word wrap for documentation files
  wordWrapForMd: true
  
  # Enable spellcheck for documentation files
  spellcheckForMd: true
  
  # Use markdown preview for .md files
  mdPreview: true
  
  # Auto-update table of contents in markdown files
  updateToc: true
```

## Core Stack
```
frontend: "React/Next.js + Vite"
styling: "Tailwind CSS + Radix UI"
state: "React Query"
backend: "Express + Drizzle ORM"
hosting: "Replit (port 5000)"
```

